#: lib/app_web/live/sandbox/utf16_decode.ex:98
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "2 bytes = 1 code unit in the [BMP^Basic Multilingual Plane] (range `U+0000` → `U+FFFF`)."
msgstr "2 octets = 1 code unit dans le [BMP^Basic Multilingual Plane] (plage `U+0000` → `U+FFFF`)."

#: lib/app_web/live/sandbox/utf16_decode.ex:104
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "4 bytes = surrogate pair for a code point beyond the [BMP^Basic Multilingual Plane]. The high code unit is in `0xD800` → `0xDBFF`, the low one in `0xDC00` → `0xDFFF`."
msgstr "4 octets = paire de surrogates pour un code point au-delà du [BMP^Basic Multilingual Plane]. Le code unit haut est dans `0xD800` → `0xDBFF`, le code unit bas dans `0xDC00` → `0xDFFF`."

#: lib/app_web/live/sandbox/windows1252_decode.ex:145
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
